{"TopicId":224792,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"How do I get ladders to survive aero-braking?","CreatedByName":"wnderer","CreatedById":102068,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-09T14:26:21Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"wnderer","CreatedById":102068,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-09T14:26:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to use aero braking. The ladders tend to explode. Is there a way to protect them from the heat?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-09T18:42:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh. I don\u0027t remember ever having this problem. What does your design look like? Is the heat shield not covering the ladder?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wnderer","CreatedById":102068,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-09T21:41:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are old threads on the topic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022135011\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed442702198\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/113662-increase-the-heat-tolerance-for-the-shrouded-ladders/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:192px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022142846\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5808384637\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/110622-overheating-ladders/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:192px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI copied the ladders to a new directory and made my own high temperature ladders by changing:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmaxTemp = 2000 //= 3200\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 to\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 maxTemp = 4000 //= 5200\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll see if that works.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"king of nowhere","CreatedById":204876,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-12T14:46:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nputting them in less exposed parts of the spacecraft may help. use a retractable version that, when retracted, is behind some more tolerant part\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Iapetus7342","CreatedById":233205,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-12T16:46:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthat\u0027s the neat part, you don\u0027t\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all seriousness just put the ladders somewhere where the heat can\u0027t reach. Use the retractable ladders too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-05-12T16:46:51Z\u0022 title=\u002205/12/2024 04:46  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022May 12\u0022\u003EMay 12\u003C/time\u003E by Iapetus7342\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Emy spelling is slightly rusty, so i fixed it\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-14T16:18:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224388371\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022224792\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221715290888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102068\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wnderer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/9/2024 at 5:41 PM, wnderer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are old threads on the topic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich relate to old versions of the game and may no longer be even valid. \u00A0 \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwaster","CreatedById":71262,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-14T23:31:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs Deadly Reentry installed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}